4 (5) (a) "Manufacturer" means a person or company that:
5 (a)(i) except as provided in subsection (5)(b), is engaged in the business of manufacturing a device
6 for consumer use;
7 (b)(ii) (i)(A) holds the patents for the device it manufactures; or
